extendedInfo.description: Nutrition / Fitness / BeautyTranquil Edge is excited to be engaged in supplying our customers with quality products such as ARTISTRY skin care & beauty; XS Energy; NUTRILITE organic health supplements; LEGACY of CLEAN household goods; and RIBBON gift collections.Several partner stores such as Bass Pro and Sears offer discounts through our site. Wireless discounts are also available. Artistry is proud to sponsor Miss America and Kurt Warner is a spokesperson for Nutrilite.Through the website you'll have the opportunity to purchase products and start your own business to bring your dreams to life.
